  "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><section style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px\"><h1 id=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 1em; border-bottom: 2px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em auto 1em; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0\" data-heading=\"true\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">璇玑枢，助力学术成长，点亮科研之路</strong></h1><section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">  <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"璇玑枢\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQiaFnHeBCs7xpwn7nA5icgHYLcsrWEbajjxSLMRBhIhhFqj8m9VSAP0vkAcnS2O3PbKUic5H1M2xKpDicyUic7d2iaqvJiaVDZWiacaLfQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"期刊介绍，论文润色，深度学习，人工智能\" data-id=\"MzY4OTE0NjQwMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"2\">  </mp-common-profile></section><section>  <span leaf=\"\"><br></span></section><p style=\"display: none;\">  <mp-style-type data-value=\"3\">  </mp-style-type></p><section style=\"background:#f3f3f3;padding:18px 20px 14px 20px;margin:16px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 20px;line-height: 1.6;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none;display: inline-block;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzY4OTE0NjQwMA==&mid=2247485611&idx=1&sn=e1f0e99a075476bd4b9e4ad40a3adccf&source=41&poc_token=HLtbuWmjCxPZuZHXYo-qKhtwRiz7oN3d1HegSgJG\" textvalue=\"科研期刊分类合集（持续更新）\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">科研期刊分类合集（持续更新）</a></span><section style=\"width:72px;height:3px;background:#2b6ff2;margin:10px 0 12px 0;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></section><section style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:#9aa0a6;\"><span leaf=\"\">合集对已介绍的多本科研期刊按研究方向与期刊定位进行汇总与分类。</span></section></section><figure style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"null\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Bps2mXQvSQh8aXFGibCs9kWRMExeJuUjW5fxtZJbvVpcy7F3z3LHC2ibmImTrBcQQSdEMUfMvXzjDsSKdkicooibzqa1ic2xLbf1L3M5zzDqdoSU/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px\"><figcaption style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\"></figcaption></figure><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Computers（TC）</strong> 是由 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Computer Society</strong> 出版的国际学术期刊，主要面向 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机体系结构、并行与分布式计算、计算系统设计等领域</strong>的理论方法与系统研究。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">该期刊创刊于 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">1952 年</strong>，是计算机领域历史最悠久的 IEEE Transactions 期刊之一，长期关注 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机硬件体系结构与系统设计相关技术的发展</strong>。 ([意得辑][1])</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">TC 的核心定位非常明确：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">发表在计算机体系结构、计算系统与硬件设计领域具有理论深度与工程价值的原创研究成果</strong>，推动计算系统性能、效率与可靠性的提升。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">在计算机体系结构研究体系中，IEEE Transactions on Computers 常被视为 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机硬件与系统方向具有代表性的 IEEE Transactions 期刊之一</strong>，其整体定位大致相当于：</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机体系结构与系统设计领域的重要 Transactions 期刊</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">长期以来，该期刊被 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">SCIE 收录</strong>，并在 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">中科院期刊分区（2025年3月最新升级版）</strong>中位于 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机科学大类 3区</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">期刊官网：https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/RecentIssue.jsp?punumber=12</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">Index：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">SCIE / Scopus</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">期刊类型：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">Research Articles（研究论文为主）</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">开放获取：<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">No（非 OA）</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">学科分区（以页面最新说明为准）：<ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• JCR（2024-2025 最新版）：</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">COMPUTER SCIENCE, HARDWARE & ARCHITECTURE</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">COMPUTER SCIENCE, THEORY & METHODS</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">ENGINEERING, ELECTRICAL & ELECTRONIC</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 中科院期刊分区（2025年3月最新升级版）：</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">大类：计算机科学 3区</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">小类：COMPUTER SCIENCE, HARDWARE & ARCHITECTURE 3区；COMPUTER SCIENCE, THEORY & METHODS 3区；ENGINEERING, ELECTRICAL & ELECTRONIC 3区</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">Top 期刊：否；综述期刊：否</strong></li></ul></p><figure style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; col