family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">研究论文为主</strong></li></ul></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">期刊整体发文数量较为稳定，对论文的 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">理论贡献、系统设计创新与实验验证</strong>要求较高。</p><h2 id=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">征稿范围</h2><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Computers（TC）</strong> 主要关注 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机体系结构与计算系统相关研究</strong>，包括但不限于以下方向：<h3 id=\"6\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI