elvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">问题定义清晰、方法严谨、实验可复现</strong></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">投稿系统：https://mc.manuscriptcentral.com/tc</p><h2 id=\"5\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">期刊总结</h2>总体来看，<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Computers（TC）</strong> 是 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算机体系结构与计算系统研究领域历史悠久的重要 IEEE Transactions 期刊之一</strong>。<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">凭借 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Computer Society 出版背景与长期稳定的学术影响力</strong>，该期刊持续汇聚 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">处理器架构、并行计算与计算系统优化</strong>等方向的研究成果。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">在计算机体系结构研究社区中，TC 仍然是 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">具有代表性的计算系统研究期刊平台之一</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">璇玑枢，我以渺小，与你同行——愿你的计算架构与系统创新，在每一次性能突破中被更高效地实现。</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">[1]: https://www.editage.cn/research-solutions/journal/ieee-transactions-on-comp